short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: RPA Genie Extension to interact with the Chrome browser

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: RPA Genie can use this extension to work coherently with the Chrome browser to enable the smooth detection of UI elements and provide users with opportunities for seamless development of web-based automation using RPA Genie Studio.
